name: Training Batch
query:
select `tabEmployee`.first_name,
`tabEmployee`.date_of_birth,
`tabEmployee`.cell_number,
`tabEmployee`.default_shift as shift,
`tabJob Applicant`.Qualification,
`tabJob Applicant`.father_name,
`tabSalary Slip`.gross_pay as CTC
from `tabEmployee`,`tabJob Applicant`,`tabSalary Slip`;
